[!!!] Generate and set SECRET_KEY in .env before first deploy
      → python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_hex(32))"

[!!!] Set POSTGRES_PASS to a strong unique password in .env

[!!!] Set DASHBOARD_PASSWORD_HASH via CLI generator before exposing :8501
      → python -m warden.analytics.auth

[!!!] Replace placeholder app/Dockerfile with real application code
      → Current file contains only the integration stub / safe_prompt() example

[!!!] Replace placeholder analytics/Dockerfile with real analytics API
      → Current service returns only a health-check stub on :8002

[!!]  Enable HTTPS on Nginx (TLS termination)
      → Uncomment HTTPS server block in warden/nginx/nginx.conf
      → Provision Let's Encrypt certificate (certbot) or supply .pem files
      → Redirect HTTP → HTTPS

[!!]  Set ENV=production in .env and audit all dev-mode code paths

[!!]  Rotate ANTHROPIC_API_KEY regularly; document rotation procedure

[!!]  Confirm Docker Desktop RAM allocation ≥ 4 GB before first build
      → MiniLM model load requires ~400 MB RAM per warden container replica

